cmm0eqyr20001s2sca7eokc24	cmm0eqyqm0000s2scocwcsg1i	1.1	non_compliant	75	Out of the four images found on the provided URL, two do not have alternative text (alt attribute). The first image has an alt attribute but its value is empty, which does not provide any meaningful information for screen readers or users with visual impairments. The second image is an SVG and does not have an alt attribute at all. These issues indicate a lack of proper implementation of the requirement for alternative text for images that convey important information.	[{"type": "issue", "message": "Image with empty alt attribute: <img id=\\"CybotCookiebotDialogPoweredbyImage\\" src=\\"...\\" alt=\\"\\">"}, {"type": "issue", "message": "SVG image without alt attribute: <svg viewBox=\\"0 0 843 248\\" aria-hidden=\\"true\\" xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\">"}]	["Provide meaningful alternative text for all images that convey important information to ensure accessibility for users with visual impairments.", "Ensure that the alt attribute is not empty and provides a description of the image content.", "For SVG images, include an alt attribute with a description of the image content."]	ai	4	\N
cmm0eqyr20002s2scaxc1twfv	cmm0eqyqm0000s2scocwcsg1i	1.2	non_compliant	75	While a majority of the images on the provided URL seem to have appropriate alt attributes, two images do not have them. Specifically, the first image has an empty alt attribute ("alt="""), and the second image is an SVG without any alt attribute at all. These issues are indicative of non-compliance with criterion 1.2 (Level A) of RGAA 4.1.	[{"type": "issue", "message": "Image with id \\"CybotCookiebotDialogPoweredbyImage\\" has an empty alt attribute (\\"alt=''\\")."}, {"type": "issue", "message": "The SVG image does not have an alt attribute."}]	["Ensure that all images, including decorative ones, have appropriate and descriptive alt attributes to improve accessibility for screen reader users.", "For the SVG image, add an alt attribute with a meaningful description or use aria-hidden=\\"true\\" if it is purely decorative."]	ai	25	\N
