cmm0eqyr2000as2sck2kcy26z	cmm0eqyqm0000s2scocwcsg1i	2.1	non_compliant	75	Out of the four frames found on the website, none of them have a title attribute set. According to RGAA 4.1 Criterion 2.1 (Level A), each frame should have a title. Although there is no concrete evidence that these frames are functional or essential for the content understanding, the lack of titles can potentially create confusion for users who rely on assistive technologies.	[{"type": "issue", "message": "Frames do not have titles"}]	["Set a title attribute for each frame to provide context and improve accessibility."]	ai	4	\N
